each man's death diminishes me for i am involved in mankind therefore send not to know for whom the bell tolls it tolls for thee so in other words every man's death is also a little death within me uh um you know i had a friend down in cornwall i would visit uh on occasion and uh he died and of course i've lost that relationship so something in me has

