they would have been you know late 20s 30s so very close to him in age he said that the sangha that's the the order of monks and nuns um uh felt empty without them see so that's the other side that's that that's the business of no man is an island but now but but we've got this uh more negative side which is really about um the grief that we feel so uh you know this um

